{"text_id":245157,"tokens":["We"," investigate"," the"," presence"," of"," light"," nuclei"," in"," galactic"," globular"," clusters",","," focusing"," on"," the"," self","-","en","richment"," scenario"," and"," its"," implications"," for"," nucle","os","ynthesis","."," Motiv","ated"," by"," the"," long","-","standing"," question"," of"," how"," these"," clusters"," formed"," and"," evolved",","," we"," aim"," to"," constrain"," the"," self","-","en","richment"," scenario",","," which"," proposes"," that"," globular"," clusters"," were"," able"," to"," self","-","enrich"," through"," the"," nucle","osy","nthetic"," products"," of"," their"," own"," stars","."," Using"," a"," combination"," of"," stellar"," evolution"," models"," and"," nucle","os","ynthesis"," calculations",","," we"," explore"," the"," production"," of"," light"," nuclei",","," such"," as"," He",","," Li",","," and"," C",","," within"," globular"," clusters","."," Our"," results"," show"," that"," the"," self","-","en","richment"," scenario"," struggles"," to"," reproduce"," the"," observed"," abundance"," patterns"," of"," these"," elements",","," suggesting"," that"," external"," sources"," of"," enrichment"," are"," necessary"," to"," explain"," the"," chemical"," composition"," of"," globular"," clusters","."," We"," discuss"," the"," implications"," of"," our"," findings"," for"," our"," understanding"," of"," globular"," cluster"," formation"," and"," evolution",","," highlighting"," the"," need"," for"," a"," more"," complex"," and"," nuanced"," picture"," of"," these"," systems","."," Our"," study"," provides"," new"," insights"," into"," the"," nucle","osy","nthetic"," history"," of"," globular"," clusters",","," and"," sheds"," light"," on"," the"," role"," of"," self","-","en","richment"," in"," shaping"," their"," chemical"," properties","."],"sub_source":"arxiv","model":"llama3-70b","label":1}